data.description: Step into the welcoming ambiance of 2215 N Bolivar Rd. This conveniently located residence invites you with an oversized open concept living room, a cozy and inviting kitchen, and hardwood floors that grace most of the home. Offering a comfortable living space, the home comprises 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a versatile bonus room with the potential for use as a third bedroom or office. The property boasts a fenced backyard, along with the added convenience of a detached garage and carport. Notably, a new roof was installed in 2021.
